For each site, check the `installation_date` relative to the range of `count_date`:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
bike_data %>%
  group_by(site_name, installation_date) %>%
  summarise(min_count_date = min(count_date), max_count_date = max(count_date),
            .groups = "drop") %>%
  gt()
```

